title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (25): Multilingual and Multitask Learning
description:
This lecture (by Graham Neubig) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Multitask Learning
* Domain Adaptation
* Multilingual Learning

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-25-multitask.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/4AQbrT-GD2k

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
